  "description": "&lt;div style=\"font-family:&amp;quot;Avenir Next W01&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next W00&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next&amp;quot;, Avenir, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size:16px;\"&gt;&lt;div style=\"margin-bottom:3rem;\"&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div style=\"overflow:auto; padding-bottom:0.375rem; max-width:100%; display:inherit;\"&gt;&lt;p style=\"margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:1.5rem;\"&gt;Ord. No. 1552-A-90 (1991) and Ord. No. 1465-97 (1997) outline the parking restrictions for seven (7) distinct parking districts in Downtown Cleveland. The ordinances include regulations regarding parking signage, monetary rates, screening/landscaping, etc. Copies of these ordinances can be found in the City Record or through the City Council Archives.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\"margin-bottom:3rem; font-family:&amp;quot;Avenir Next W01&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next W00&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next&amp;quot;, Avenir, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size:16px;\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\"font-family:&amp;quot;Avenir Next W01&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next W00&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next&amp;quot;, Avenir, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size:16px;\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\"margin-bottom:3rem; display:inherit; font-family:&amp;quot;Avenir Next W01&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next W00&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next&amp;quot;, Avenir, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size:16px;\"&gt;&lt;div style=\"margin-bottom:3rem; display:inherit;\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;",
